com.precog.client

Interface Format

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelimitedFormat, JsonFormat

    public interface Format
    Used to specify the format of some data to be inserted into Precog. This is effectively a closed type hierarchy, supporting JSON (JsonFormat) and CSV (DelimitedFormat).
    Author:
    Tom Switzer
